<div1 type="letter">

<pb facs="nei.j4c.48.19a" />

<opener>
<note>
Skyrim Farm  4-5-'66
</note>
<dateline>Tuesday, April 5, '66.</dateline>


<salute>Dear Slade:</salute>
</opener>
<p>Of course, as I know now, it was the Davenport letters that troubled me when I wrote you the other day! I had not thanked you for wanting to share them with me. Many, many thanks! Yes, I wish I could have known the man too.</p>

<p>I'm embarassed by offered engagments. The dates don't make a workable pattern, and I must refuse 

<note type="authorial">(over)</note>

<pb facs="nei.j4c.48.19"/>
<fw type="authorial">-<del>2</del>-2-</fw>
<fw type="curatorial"><del/></fw>

<del>one</del><add>two</add> I'd greatly enjoy.</p>
<closer>
<salute>With the old affection &#8212;</salute>

<signed>John Neihardt</signed>
</closer>

<fw type="curatorial">19</fw>

</div1>
